{"tid":1174481,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解城巴app唔可以好似九巴app咁user friendly??","createTime":"2019-05-28T01:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T09:19:57.000Z","uid":103888,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c71e8a861d97f5bc6c0bdf36af9022afe0ce2318","tid":1174481,"uid":103888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:14:46.000Z","msg":"一打開城巴app已經即刻<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">彈咗個廣告</span></span>出黎（要等十秒個隻）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDllm我趕時間先要睇下幾時有車<br />\n要知道打工仔搭巴士係爭分奪秒<br />\n十秒足已令你走咗一班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇下不同站到站時間會飛入另一頁面<br />\nLoad嚟load去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>字又多</strong></span><br />\n趕時間個陣死得<br />\n到你搵到架車嘅資訊架車已經走埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然九巴都有廣告<br />\n但撳個x就可以即去下個頁面<br />\n一開app已經講埋你知附近有咩車<br />\n幾時有車<br />\n上一站下一站幾時到都係同一頁面唔會走黎走去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一目了然</span><br />\n真真正正user friendly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝頭早趕頭趕命人士嘅恩物<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九巴👍🏻</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />城巴👎</span>"},{"pid":"e0e2d66de25a55f73e06d316cbdcb95e21eccd17","tid":1174481,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE11POL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE11POL.png&h=5f84bfc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"624a110272a8aef6bc0a85919bd2fc301b